There is a pdfcrop at
http://pdfcrop.sourceforge.net/
but the one I have installed on Ubuntu is this one:
https://www.ctan.org/tex-archive/support/pdfcrop
Install it with:

mkdir -p $HOME/bin/`uname`-`uname -m`
cd $HOME/bin/`uname`-`uname -m`
wget http://mirrors.ctan.org/support/pdfcrop/pdfcrop.pl -O pdfcrop
chmod +x pdfcrop
